To use Enhance on the cluster,

0) adapt the environment, put any files you need (e.g. code) in the work directory
1) upload the environment to grid storage with the upload script in the root directory
2) copy the contents of this directory to a location of your choosing
   - adapt the jdl to include the number of jobs and the environment location on the grid
   - adapt the enhance_worker script to perform the actions you need
3) submit the job
